{"tid":1831814,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有位澳洲記者想大家幫手","createTime":"2020-01-20T16:23:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-20T17:10:45.000Z","uid":324847,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"add9e4f69a2360ca562c329c519791b4713c3ff5","tid":1831814,"uid":324847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T16:23:47.000Z","msg":"Avi Yemini 由上年8月開始一直都見佢出唔同關於香港嘅報道<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dDJeffT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdDJeffT.png&h=195d5307&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n之前佢仲係中環質問過葉劉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4aZXXuA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4aZXXuA.png&h=a8cd78eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n依家佢話會一直stand with Hong Kong直到五大訴求 缺一不可 但係佢有啲嘢要大家幫手<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/4wu_fZOAc9w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F4wu_fZOAc9w&d=%2F7nbYOXxgzDTTn%2FAx8VV9zv6TERBNTdTd%2BiGQaA%2FLRg%3D&h=ff8835f7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/4wu_fZOAc9w</a><br />\n<br />\n雖然不外乎都係錢 但係佢真係有付出過 相信睇開YouTube 蘋果嘅人都應該識佢 大家幫到手咪幫囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>五大訴求<br />\n缺一不可</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"96bad08b61c3e7d7e0b9add9be3c64794ffb3d9f","tid":1831814,"uid":324847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T16:24:35.000Z","msg":"p牌推唔到都自推10次<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc6384b5b74d0e567873b45a22747657784e357a","tid":1831814,"uid":324847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T16:25:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"> 黑警死全家</span>"},{"pid":"854025aa37312785af61b223f8a52d36b413e3ea","tid":1831814,"uid":324847,"